{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_48","type":"agent_message","text":"`amendSlf4jConfig` itself only reads `akka.loggers` and `akka.logging-filter` from the already-built config. So the real bug is earlier: by the time `ActorSystem.Settings` gets that config, it apparently still lacks the merged Akka defaults. I’m tracing the config construction path now rather than adding more blind resource entries."}}
